.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_SOURCE_GET_USER_DATA 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_source_get_user_data
.Nd retrieve user data from a drag source session
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft void *
.Fn x11dnd_source_get_user_data "X11DndSourceSession *sess"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_source_get_user_data
returns the
.Fa user_data
pointer that was passed to
.Xr x11dnd_start_drag 3
when the session was created.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The user data pointer, or
.Dv NULL
if none was set.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_start_drag 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_target_get_user_data 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
